<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <style>
        /* Print Settings */
        @page {
            size: A4;
            margin: 0;
        }

        @media print {
            * {
                -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact !important;
                print-color-adjust: exact !important;
            }
        }

        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            font-size: 12px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            color: #1e293b;
            background-color: #fff;
            width: 794px;
            max-width: 794px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        /* Header - Solid Color for Print */
        .header {
            background-color: #6366f1;
            color: white;
            padding: 32px 40px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: flex-start;
        }

        .header-left h1 {
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
        }

        .header-left p {
            font-size: 14px;
            opacity: 0.9;
            font-weight: 400;
        }

        .header-right {
            text-align: right;
        }

        .budget-number {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
            padding: 14px 24px;
            border-radius: 12px;
        }

        .budget-number-label {
            font-size: 10px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1.5px;
            opacity: 0.85;
            margin-bottom: 2px;
        }

        .budget-number-value {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            font-family: 'SF Mono', Monaco, monospace;
        }

        /* Status Badge */
        .status-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 6px 16px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-size: 11px;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            margin-top: 12px;
        }

        .status-pendente {
            background: #fef3c7;
            color: #92400e;
        }

        .status-aprovado {
            background: #d1fae5;
            color: #065f46;
        }

        .status-recusado {
            background: #fee2e2;
            color: #991b1b;
        }

        .status-vencido {
            background: #f1f5f9;
            color: #64748b;
        }

        .status-convertido {
            background: #ede9fe;
            color: #5b21b6;
        }

        /* Content Container */
        .content {
            padding: 32px 40px;
        }

        /* Date Info */
        .date-info {
            display: flex;
            gap: 48px;
            margin-bottom: 28px;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }

        .date-item {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        .date-label {
            font-size: 10px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            color: #64748b;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .date-value {
            font-size: 15px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #1e293b;
        }

        /* Info Cards - Apple Style */
        .info-grid {
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 32px;
        }

        .info-card {
            flex: 1;
            background: #f8fafc;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            border-radius: 14px;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .info-card-label {
            font-size: 10px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            color: #64748b;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .info-card-value {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #1e293b;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }

        .info-card-detail {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #64748b;
            margin-top: 2px;
        }

        /* Items Table */
        .section-title {
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #1e293b;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #e2e8f0;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }

        .items-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-bottom: 28px;
        }

        .items-table th {
            background: #f8fafc;
            padding: 12px 16px;
            text-align: left;
            font-size: 10px;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            color: #64748b;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }

        .items-table th:first-child {
            border-radius: 8px 0 0 0;
        }

        .items-table th:last-child {
            border-radius: 0 8px 0 0;
            text-align: right;
        }

        .items-table th.text-center {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .items-table th.text-right {
            text-align: right;
        }

        .items-table td {
            padding: 14px 16px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f5f9;
            font-size: 13px;
        }

        .items-table td.text-center {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .items-table td.text-right {
            text-align: right;
        }

        .items-table tr:last-child td {
            border-bottom: none;
        }

        .item-name {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #1e293b;
        }

        .quantity-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #e2e8f0;
            color: #475569;
            padding: 4px 12px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 12px;
        }

        .price-muted {
            color: #64748b;
        }

        .price-bold {
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #1e293b;
        }

        /* Totals Section */
        .totals-section {
            background: #f8fafc;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            border-radius: 14px;
            padding: 20px 24px;
            margin-bottom: 28px;
        }

        .total-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 8px 0;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #64748b;
        }

        .total-row.discount {
            color: #10b981;
        }

        .total-row.final {
            border-top: 2px dashed #cbd5e1;
            margin-top: 12px;
            padding-top: 16px;
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #1e293b;
        }

        .total-row.final span:last-child {
            color: #6366f1;
        }

        /* Observations */
        .observations {
            background: #fffbeb;
            border: 1px solid #fcd34d;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 18px 20px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }

        .observations-title {
            font-size: 11px;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            color: #92400e;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .observations-text {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #78350f;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* Conditions */
        .conditions {
            background: #f8fafc;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 18px 20px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .conditions-title {
            font-size: 11px;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            color: #64748b;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .conditions-list {
            font-size: 11px;
            color: #475569;
            line-height: 2;
        }

        /* Signature Area - Page Break */
        .signature-section {
            page-break-before: auto;
            margin-top: 40px;
        }

        .signature-area {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding-top: 60px;
        }

        .signature-box {
            width: 45%;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .signature-line {
            border-top: 1px solid #94a3b8;
            padding-top: 10px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #64748b;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        /* Footer */
        .footer {
            border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            padding-top: 20px;
            margin-top: 24px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #94a3b8;
            font-size: 11px;
        }

        .footer-store {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #64748b;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }

        /* Credit Simulation Section */
        .crediario-section {
            background: #f8fafc;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            border-radius: 14px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }

        .crediario-header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            padding-bottom: 12px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }

        .crediario-title {
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #6366f1;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }

        .crediario-rate {
            background: #6366f1;
            color: white;
            padding: 6px 14px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .crediario-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .crediario-table th {
            background: #e2e8f0;
            padding: 10px 12px;
            text-align: left;
            font-size: 10px;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            color: #64748b;
        }

        .crediario-table th:first-child {
            border-radius: 6px 0 0 0;
        }

        .crediario-table th:last-child {
            border-radius: 0 6px 0 0;
        }

        .crediario-table td {
            padding: 10px 12px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            font-size: 12px;
        }

        .crediario-table tr:last-child td {
            border-bottom: none;
        }

        .parcelas-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #6366f1;
            color: white;
            padding: 4px 10px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 11px;
        }

        .juros-col {
            color: #f59e0b;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .amortization-notice {
            background: #d1fae5;
            border: 1px solid #10b981;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 14px 16px;
        }

        .amortization-title {
            font-size: 11px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #065f46;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }

        .amortization-text {
            font-size: 11px;
            color: #047857;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="header">
        <div class="header-left">
            <h1>ORÇAMENTO</h1>
            <p>Proposta Comercial</p>
        </div>
        <div class="header-right">
            <div class="budget-number">
                <div class="budget-number-label">Código</div>
                <div class="budget-number-value">{{numero}}</div>
            </div>
            <div class="status-badge status-{{status}}">{{statusLabel}}</div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Content -->
    <div class="content">
        <!-- Date Info -->
        <div class="date-info">
            <div class="date-item">
                <span class="date-label">Data de Emissão</span>
                <span class="date-value">{{dataEmissao}}</span>
            </div>
            {{#if validadeAte}}
            <div class="date-item">
                <span class="date-label">Válido Até</span>
                <span class="date-value">{{validadeAte}}</span>
            </div>
            {{/if}}
        </div>

        <!-- Info Cards -->
        <div class="info-grid">
            <div class="info-card">
                <div class="info-card-label">Cliente</div>
                <div class="info-card-value">{{cliente.nome}}</div>
                {{#if cliente.cpfCnpj}}
                <div class="info-card-detail">CPF/CNPJ: {{cliente.cpfCnpj}}</div>
                {{/if}}
                {{#if cliente.telefone}}
                <div class="info-card-detail">Tel: {{cliente.telefone}}</div>
                {{/if}}
            </div>
            <div class="info-card">
                <div class="info-card-label">Loja</div>
                <div class="info-card-value">{{loja.nome}}</div>
                {{#if loja.endereco}}
                <div class="info-card-detail">{{loja.endereco}}</div>
                {{/if}}
                {{#if loja.telefone}}
                <div class="info-card-detail">Tel: {{loja.telefone}}</div>
                {{/if}}
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Items Table -->
        <div class="section-title">Itens do Orçamento</div>
        <table class="items-table">
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th style="width: 45%">Produto</th>
                    <th class="text-center" style="width: 15%">Qtd</th>
                    <th class="text-right" style="width: 20%">Valor Unit.</th>
                    <th class="text-right" style="width: 20%">Subtotal</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                {{#each itens}}
                <tr>
                    <td>
                        <span class="item-name">{{descricao}}</span>
                    </td>
                    <td class="text-center">
                        <span class="quantity-badge">{{quantidade}}</span>
                    </td>
                    <td class="text-right price-muted">R$ {{precoUnit}}</td>
                    <td class="text-right price-bold">R$ {{subtotal}}</td>
                </tr>
                {{/each}}
            </tbody>
        </table>

        <!-- Totals -->
        <div class="totals-section">
            {{#if desconto}}
            <div class="total-row">
                <span>Subtotal</span>
                <span>R$ {{subtotalFormatted}}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="total-row discount">
                <span>Desconto</span>
                <span>- R$ {{descontoFormatted}}</span>
            </div>
            {{/if}}
            <div class="total-row final">
                <span>TOTAL</span>
                <span>R$ {{totalFormatted}}</span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Observations -->
        {{#if observacoes}}
        <div class="observations">
            <div class="observations-title">Observações</div>
            <div class="observations-text">{{observacoes}}</div>
        </div>
        {{/if}}

        <!-- Conditions -->
        <div class="conditions">
            <div class="conditions-title">Condições Gerais</div>
            <div class="conditions-list">
                • Este orçamento tem validade de acordo com a data especificada acima.<br>
                • Preços e condições sujeitos a alteração sem aviso prévio após o vencimento.<br>
                • Prazo de entrega a combinar conforme disponibilidade de estoque.<br>
                • Formas de pagamento: Dinheiro, PIX, Cartão de Crédito/Débito, Crediário.
            </div>
        </div>

        {{#if simulacaoCredito}}
        <!-- Credit Simulation -->
        <div class="crediario-section">
            <div class="crediario-header">
                <div class="crediario-title">Condições de Pagamento – Crediário</div>
                <div class="crediario-rate">{{taxaMensalFormatada}} a.m.</div>
            </div>

            <table class="crediario-table">
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Parcelas</th>
                        <th>Valor da Parcela</th>
                        <th>Total Financiado</th>
                        <th>Juros Totais</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    {{#each simulacaoCredito}}
                    <tr>
                        <td><span class="parcelas-badge">{{parcelas}}x</span></td>
                        <td><strong>R$ {{valorParcela}}</strong></td>
                        <td>R$ {{totalFinanciado}}</td>
                        <td class="juros-col">R$ {{jurosTotais}} ({{percentualJuros}}%)</td>
                    </tr>
                    {{/each}}
                </tbody>
            </table>

            <div class="amortization-notice">
                <div class="amortization-title">Amortização Disponível</div>
                <div class="amortization-text">
                    Em caso de pagamentos antecipados (parciais ou totais), os juros são automaticamente recalculados,
                    reduzindo o total final da dívida. Quanto antes você pagar, menos juros paga.
                    Esta condição é válida durante todo o período do financiamento.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        {{/if}}

        <!-- Signature Area -->
        <div class="signature-section">
            <div class="signature-area">
                <div class="signature-box">
                    <div class="signature-line">Assinatura do Cliente</div>
                </div>
                <div class="signature-box">
                    <div class="signature-line">Assinatura do Vendedor</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Footer -->
        <div class="footer">
            <div class="footer-store">{{loja.nome}}</div>
            <div>Obrigado pela preferência! Em caso de dúvidas, entre em contato.</div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>